TITLE: Saving Form Data to a Model (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: This shows how to save the form's data to a model using Eloquent.  It utilizes the `Post::create()` method to create a new post record in the database using the validated form data retrieved by `$this->form->getState()`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/filamentphp/filament/blob/3.x/packages/forms/docs/08-adding-a-form-to-a-livewire-component.md#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use App\Models\Post;

public function create(): void
{
