TITLE: Customize Relation Manager Form (Filament)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet customizes the form within the relation manager, defining the fields that can be edited for related records. It uses Filament's form builder to create a text input field for the 'description' attribute.  The form expects a Filament\Forms\Form instance as input and returns a configured Form instance.
