TITLE: Creating and Configuring Bulk Actions (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to create a bulk action with specific behavior, in this case, deleting selected records. It uses `BulkAction::make()` to create a 'delete' action. It also utilizes the `requiresConfirmation()` method to ensure the user confirms before executing and then performs a delete for each of the selected records in the action callback using `action()`. The dependencies include BulkAction and Collection facades.
