TITLE: Filtering Widget Data - Interacting with Filters (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to use the `InteractsWithPageFilters` trait in a widget class to access the raw data from the filters form using the `$this->filters` property, to filter BlogPost data by start and end dates.
