TITLE: Color Picker Validation - PHP
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to validate the color picker values using Laravel's validation rules and regular expressions. Each color format (HEX, HSL, RGB, RGBA) has a corresponding regex to ensure the input matches the expected format.
