TITLE: Adding suffix action to a TextEntry in Filament
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates how to add a suffix action to a Filament TextEntry. It creates an action named 'copyCostToPrice', sets its icon, requires confirmation, and defines a function that copies the 'cost' value to the 'price' attribute of a Product record. The action is triggered on the 'cost' TextEntry.
