TITLE: OrderProduct Pivot Model - PHP
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines the `OrderProduct` pivot model, including relationships to the `Order` and `Product` models.  It's used with a `BelongsToMany` relationship and has `$incrementing = true` to ensure Filament tracks primary keys. This model also defines the inverse relationships to `Order` and `Product`.
