TITLE: Using Simple Pagination in Filament Table (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to implement simple pagination in a Filament table by overriding the `paginateTableQuery()` method in the Livewire component.  It returns a `Paginator` instance from the query.
