TITLE: Adding Dynamic Tooltips
DESCRIPTION: Specifies a dynamic tooltip for a TextEntry using a closure.  The closure has access to the current infolist record. The example depends on the `Filament\Infolists\Components\TextEntry` class and `Illuminate\Database\Eloquent\Model`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/filamentphp/filament/blob/3.x/packages/infolists/docs/03-entries/01-getting-started.md#_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Filament\Infolists\Components\TextEntry;
use Illuminate\Database\Eloquent\Model;

TextEntry::make('title')
    ->tooltip(fn (Model $record): string => "By {$record->author->name}")
```

